Let's go

Nu buc phi gii thch Docker trong mt cu ngn gn, ta c th ni Docker l mt nn tng gip n gin ho qu trnh build, run, qun l, v phn phi app ca bn. Docker lm c iu ny v n m phng/ o ho h iu hnh m n ang chy trn.

Phin bn u tin ca docker c pht hnh vo nm 2013.

Docker c pht trin s dng ngn ng GO.

Bt k mt pht minh no c sinh ra cng hng n vic gii quyt mt vn  no . Vy chng ta hy cng xem vn , v cch m Docker gii quyt nh th no nh!

### Vn 

t trng hp, bn c 3 app khc nhau vit bng Python, v bn d nh s ci n trn mt server duy nht.

C iu, mi app li s dng mt version khc nhau ca Python, ng thi cc dependencies (l cc th vin, package m app ng dng) gia cc app cng khc nhau.

R rng, chng ta khng th ci nhiu version ca Python trn cng mt my tnh ( y l server), iu ny ngn cn chng ta t c mc tiu ban u,  l: ci c 3 app trn trn cng mt server.

### Hng gii quyt

#### Phng n 1: Khng dng Docker

Vi phng n ny, ta c th setup 3 server - mi server s run mt app Python kia; hoc setup 1 server  kho  host v run 1 lc 3 virtual machine (my o) - mi my o s run mt app Python kia. Nh vy ta c th ci cc version nhau ca Python - mi my mt version cng vi cc package v th vin i cng vi cc version .

Vi phng n ny, gi thnh  sm sa thit b v maintain (duy tr, bo dng) c th s kh cao.

#### Phng n 2: S dng Docker

Cng xem Docker gii quyt bi ton ny trit  v li chi ph nh th no nh.

 hiu c iu ny, trc tin chng ta cn nm nguyn l hot ng ca Docker.

Server hay my tnh m Docker c install v running trn n, ta gi n l Docker Host, hay n gin l Host.

Mi khi bn deploy mt app no  ln host, host s to mt logical entity (mt thc th logic) trn host  run cha app ca bn. Trong Docker, ta gi_logical entity_ ny l Docker Container, hay c th gi tt l Container.

![](blob:https://wordtohtml.net/7ec11002-7f3b-4e45-8b5e-bd3fb30a422b)

Khc vi VMWare (mt virtual machine), Docker Container khng c mt h iu hnh no chy trong n c. Nhng n k tha t h iu hnh (HH ca host) cc process table, network interfaces v file system mount points. Trong khi ti nguyn kernel (li) ca h iu hnh c chia n tt c cc Container theo nhu cu s dng.

iu ny cho php cc Container c lp vi nhau khi  trn cng mt Host. Chnh v th m cc Container vi cc app khc nhau c yu cu, dependencies khc nhau c th cng chy song song trn mt host duy nht vi iu kin cc app ny yu cu cng mt loi h iu hnh.

Tm gn, khc vi Virtual machine, Docker m phng/ o ho h iu hnh ca host, hn l o ho phn cng ca host - cch m Virtual machine lm

## u v nhc khi s dng Docker

### u im

*   Docker h tr rt nhiu app khc nhau vi cc yu cu v dependencies khc nhau, cho php chng cng chy trn mt host, vi iu kin l cc app yu cu cng 1 h iu hnh
*   Ti u ho lu tr. Rt nhiu app c th cng c cha ti cng mt host, v size ca Container cng rt nh, ch vi MB.
*   Container khng cha c 1 h iu hnh trong n, ng ngha vi vic n ch tiu tn rt t b nh so vi Virtual Machine. v do  cng s s gim c thi gian khi ng container i r rt, ch tiu tns vi so vi vi pht nh trn Virtual Machine.
*   Tit kim chi ph. Docker ch yu cu ti nguyn chy chnh app  v rt t ti nguyn cho bn thn Docker, nn bn s tit kim rt nhiu chi ph setup phn cng server.

### Nhc im

Nu mi app yu cu mt h iu hnh khc nhau th chng khng th cng c host trn mt Docker Host. Ly v d ta c 4 apps, 3 app chy trn nn Linux, 1 app Windows, lc ny 3 apps Linux c th c host trn chung mt Docker Host, trong khi cu WIndows app kia s cn phi c ci trn mt Docker Host khc.

## Cu to ca Docker

Docker Engine l phn ct li ca Docker, chu trch nhim cho ton b chc nng ca nn tng Docker.

Docker Engine cng l mt phn mm pht trin trn m hnh client-server, n gm c 3 phn

*   Server
*   REST API
*   Client

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Server chy mt daemon (ta c th hiu nh mt service) tn l dockerd. Dockerd ph trch vic to v qun l_Docker Images_,_Containers_,_Networks_ v_Volumes_ ca nn tng Docker.

REST API ch ra cch thc m app giao tip vi Servers

The Client n gin l mt giao din cho php chng ta giao tip vi Docker thng qua dng lnh.

### Mt vi thut ng trong Docker

Ngoi Docker Containers,**Docker Image** cng l mt khi nim quan trng cc bn s tip xc thng xuyn khi lm vic vi Docker.

**Docker Image** l mt b template cha app ca bn v tt c cc dependencies/ packages m app yu cu.

Cn**Docker Container**, nh  ni  phn u, l mt thc th logic, ni chnh xc hn th n thc cht l mt th chy Docker Image.

Cn**Docker Hub**? Docker Hub l mt kho cha chnh thng, ni bn c th tm thy cc Docker Images c chia s  y.

Docker Hub cng l mt ni cho php bn lu tr Docker images ca ng dng ca bn (nu bn mun). Bn c th set n l public  mi ngi c th tm kim hay private ty vo mc ch s dng.

_Lu _: Free Account trn Dcoker Hub gii hn ch 1 Docker Image set private, nu bn c nhiu Image v mun set chng private th phi ng k cc gi Account tr ph khc.

**Docker Editions** Docker c 2 phin bn gm:

*   Community Edition (CE)
*   Enterprise Edition (EE)

Community Edition ph hp cho cc c nhn hay team nh.

Khi bn l mt team ln hay mt doanh nghip cn s h lu di v m bo khi c s c xy ra th Enterprise Edition chnh l s la chn ca bn.
